### Get All Compact Discs
GET http://localhost:8080/compact-discs

### Get Compact Disc by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/compact-discs/1

### Create Compact Disc (without artist)
POST http://localhost:8080/compact-discs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Abbey Road",
  "numberOfTracks": 17
}

### Create Compact Disc with Artist
POST http://localhost:8080/compact-discs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Dark Side of the Moon",
  "numberOfTracks": 10,
  "artist": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Create Another Compact Disc
POST http://localhost:8080/compact-discs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band",
  "numberOfTracks": 13,
  "artist": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Update Compact Disc
PUT http://localhost:8080/compact-discs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Abbey Road - Remastered",
  "numberOfTracks": 17,
  "artist": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Delete Compact Disc
DELETE http://localhost:8080/compact-discs/1

### Get Non-Existent Compact Disc (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/compact-discs/999